snippet.title: Alien Hominid Invasion - OTK Games Expo 2023 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Invasion is almost upon us, and the aliens crash landed at the OTK Games Expo 2023 to share this special trailer and announce that they will be Invading Steam Next Fest from June 19th to 26th!

Get your hands on the game before launch, or be laughed out of the spaceship and go sit with the agents. Don't forget to beam on down to our Discord server during Next Fest to talk about the game with other players and give your feedback to the devs!

MORE INTEL
Wishlist on Steam: https://www.beh.gg/AHI
Official Discord: https://www.beh.gg/discord
The Behemoth on Twitter: https://www.beh.gg/tweet

Music by Patric Catani: https://patric-catani.bandcamp.com/
Trailer by Sarah O.
